<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.2">
<l>poṉpōl mañcaṉa māṭṭi yamutūṭṭip pōṉēṉ varumaḷa vippāl</l>
<l>vaṉpā raccaka ṭamiṟac cāṭi vaṭakkila kampuk kiruntu</l>
<l>miṉpōl nuṇṇiṭai yāloru kaṉṉiyai vēṟṟuru vamceytu vaitta</l>
<l>aṉpā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having bathed [you] in a radiant cerimonial bath</l>
<l rend="indent">and fed you ambrosia, I left.</l>
<l>By the time I came back, [you] had beaten the strong,</l>
<l rend="indent">heavy cart so that it broke</l>
<l rend="indent">and entered the house to the north</l>
<l>[My] Love! Who [forever] altered the body</l>
<l rend="indent">of the maiden with the lightning-like thin waist.</l>
<l>I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
